H0.text: Which four letter word beginning with B means to cause a floating log to spin rapidly by rotating it with the feet. Bump

H1.text: Which four letter word beginning with B means to cause a floating log to spin rapidly by rotating it with the feet. Bank

H2.text: Which four letter word beginning with B means to cause a floating log to spin rapidly by rotating it with the feet. Bite

H3.text: Which four letter word beginning with B means to cause a floating log to spin rapidly by rotating it with the feet. Birl

A4.text: Log rolling, sometimes called birling, is a sparring sport involving two competitors, each on one end of a free-floating log in a body of water.
